{"tid":1530631,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"張建宗：政府以開放態度審視法例應對示威","createTime":"2019-09-02T04:12:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T04:20:32.000Z","uid":216992,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"cf372fb4113d725e7f7ef75207eec709139f5fe2","tid":1530631,"uid":216992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T04:12:51.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】政務司司長張建宗被問到會否引用《緊急情況規例條例》處理反修例示威，他表示，政府會以開放態度全面審視有什麼法例可引用，但會顧及香港實際情況及整體利益。<br />\n<br />\n張建宗：「政府有能力處理現時情況，過程中警方的角色極之重要，因為是執法最重要防線，也是香港的護法者。我們要看看目前香港法律，有什麼法律可以幫助警隊工作，協助他們執行任務。我們現正全面檢視，我們以開放態度，看看香港有什麼法律用得着，但有幾個因素考慮。任何法治手段必須合法、合理、合情，以及依法辦事，由香港實際情況及整體利益出發，這一點十分重要。」<br />\n<br />\nsource: <a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=361321\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D361321&d=nh4ioWg9Uual2b2uu0vi%2FeIs%2Fr43DZ9KHrtYDEqBsnw%3D&h=529746d5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D361321&h=cc9fc6ed\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=361321</a>"},{"pid":"2d651ab21143a66011c8613023a10a7852d5c6d7","tid":1530631,"uid":216992,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T04:13:48.000Z","msg":"「我們要看看目前香港法律，有什麼法律可以幫助警隊工作，協助他們執行任務。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n想加大佢地嘅權力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"},{"pid":"e1d5db0e1bde5e41b2eb88f4c6c8882e244f55c2","tid":1530631,"uid":14918,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T04:14:50.000Z","msg":"政府可以監管多D銀行, 安插官員去銀行check數<br />\n以防有外部資金資助不威呀嘛<br />\n一有唔妥就鎖人/公司account!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ef947ac01df413f89f197f9f08f5e5a81b478c1","tid":1530631,"uid":13149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2d651ab21143a66011c8613023a10a7852d5c6d7","tid":1530631,"uid":216992,"like":1,"disli